Package de.tu_dresden.psy.inference

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    AssertionInterface
    provides means to check assertions for their distinct parts
    InferenceMap
    provides common interface for difference inference methods
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Assertion
    provides a generic assertion class
    AssertionEquivalenceClasses
    implements the management of assertion equivalence classes
    EquivalentAssertions
    implements an AssertionInterface that will take care of differently derived but otherwise equivalent assertions
    ExcessLimit
    implements methods to break operation after a given time limit has been hit
    InferenceMaps
    implements a meta-inference map that just calls all inference maps and joins the inferred assertions
    InferredAssertion
    implements an assertion interface that provides information about the inference map and premise assertions used to obtain the assertion
